          "plant_location": "Local location / area (optional)",
          "plant_icon": "Local icon, e.g. mdi:sprout",
          "plants_json": "Multiple local plants as JSON (optional)"
        },
        "description": "Optional local details are used when Boum does not expose plant names through the API. For multiple plants per pot, enter a JSON mapping, for example {\"Pflanztopf 02\":[{\"name\":\"Mint\"},{\"name\":\"Lemon verbena\"}]}. Last watered can also be derived from telemetry or Home Assistant pump actions."
